00:01:13.840 --> 00:01:17.140
Penname: Wakame@tsuaraーV

00:01:17.340 --> 00:01:18.680
"Good day! Mama!"

00:01:18.700 --> 00:01:21.160
"I was always waiting anxiously for your store’s reopening!!"

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:21.880
"In this case..."

00:01:22.020 --> 00:01:26.180
"...I’m a 22 year old man who wants to be a racer in boat racing"

00:01:26.180 --> 00:01:30.400
