00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:35.560
"To be able to enter a training institute, there exists 3 tests..."

00:01:35.700 --> 00:01:38.200
"...The approval rate is very low and it is very difficult to achieve"

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:40.080
"There also exists a corporal weight limit..."

00:01:40.340 --> 00:01:42.860
"...So then the restrictions on food and training is exhausting, but..."

00:01:43.160 --> 00:01:46.720
"...At seeing AI-chan’s videos, I always recover my enthusiasm"

00:01:46.820 --> 00:01:50.280
"Nevertheless, I also have to consider that I am 22 years old..."

00:01:50.500 --> 00:01:53.160
"What will I do if I can’t make it as a racer?"

00:01:53.160 --> 00:01:55.080
"That worry has been tormenting me"

00:01:55.240 --> 00:01:55.960
"It's because of that, that..."

00:01:55.960 --> 00:02:00.220
"...If you want, I’d like to receive a bit of encouragement by you, Ai-mama"

00:02:00.220 --> 00:02:01.160
"I feel like if you do..."

00:02:01.300 --> 00:02:04.400
"...I can increase my motivation enormously compared to how I find myself now"

00:02:04.440 --> 00:02:08.400
"I hope you can please grant me this selfish desire that I have!"

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:10.360
Mmm... I see...

00:02:10.820 --> 00:02:12.060
I see, definitely...

00:02:12.060 --> 00:02:14.840
...You worry that you’re 22 years old...

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:16.000
It's true

00:02:16.160 --> 00:02:18.400
Well, while it's true that it has a big challenge for approving...

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:19.840
...And that it’s rather worrying...

00:02:19.940 --> 00:02:21.320
Since it's your future! Right?

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:24.360
Definitely, guys worry what would happen if they’re not able to...

00:02:24.360 --> 00:02:26.060
... marry and maintain their family

00:02:26.060 --> 00:02:28.060
Right at this age, around 22 years old...

00:02:28.200 --> 00:02:32.140
...Everyone around you are getting and finding jobs, so then...

00:02:32.260 --> 00:02:34.480
...I think there's a lot of unnecessary worries, right?

00:02:34.860 --> 00:02:37.480
But, well, it doesn’t mean that you’re going to die, so then...

00:02:37.480 --> 00:02:38.600
Why don’t you do it?

00:02:38.620 --> 00:02:42.940
After all, you don’t have anything to worry that people around you are looking for jobs

00:02:42.980 --> 00:02:44.380
After all, their company can go bankrupt...

00:02:44.380 --> 00:02:46.060
...Or can be laid off during a company restructure

00:02:46.060 --> 00:02:46.720
And well...

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:47.680
...A lot of things can happen…

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:51.040
You only need to do what you want and work hard each day to get it

00:02:51.040 --> 00:02:52.940
If you do it, you have nothing to worry about!

00:02:52.940 --> 00:02:54.120
You only need to do what you want to do!

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:55.660
If the moment arrives when it turns impossible

00:02:55.820 --> 00:02:56.940
You will somehow manage it!

00:02:56.940 --> 00:02:57.940
After all, there exists a lot of professions

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:59.060
If you want...

00:02:59.160 --> 00:03:01.300
...You can come work in Snack AI

00:03:01.300 --> 00:03:02.720
How about if you come and be our waiter?

00:03:02.720 --> 00:03:03.820
Well, it's because of that...

00:03:04.020 --> 00:03:05.640
...Don’t think too much on what awaits you

00:03:05.640 --> 00:03:06.840
Only look ahead...!

00:03:06.960 --> 00:03:08.140
...And take the exam for registration!

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.780
With the feeling of: "I’ll become a boat racing racer!"!

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:12.640
Well, first off, you musn’t let other people beat you...!

00:03:12.640 --> 00:03:14.260
At least by level of feelings!

00:03:14.260 --> 00:03:15.380
Let's all do our best!

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:16.680
After all, I’ll also do my best!

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:17.780
Yes!

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:21.960
Well, if you get any other worries again, I’ll always be up for listening

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:22.620
So then, come!

00:03:22.780 --> 00:03:23.280
Yes?

00:03:23.280 --> 00:03:24.200
Come on, do your best!

00:03:24.500 --> 00:03:25.800
Good! Onto the second!

